All of the reading assignments below refer to the main textbook:
[Amazon_logo] Jacob, Bill. Linear Algebra. New York, NY: W.H. Freeman, 1990.
ISBN: 0716720310. (Out of print.)
There are two other recommended books for this course:
[Amazon_logo] Hoffman, K., and R. Kunze. Linear Algebra. 2nd ed. Upper Saddle
River, NJ: Prentice Hall, 1971. ISBN: 0135367972.
[Amazon_logo] Bretscher, O. Linear Algebra with Applications. 3rd ed. Upper
Saddle River, NJ: Prentice Hall, 2004. ISBN: 0131453343.
